{"tid":41323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"媽媽生病了，我寧願受苦既係我，可以嗎？","createTime":"2016-12-15T20:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T03:30:56.000Z","uid":15017,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"942ea2552630276a022ce27f2bd708270b0d45a6","tid":41323,"uid":15017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:46:23.000Z","msg":"媽咪驗到乳癌二期<br />\n知道左偷偷係廁所喊 <br />\n我可以用我既生命換佢既生命<br />\n點解要咁對佢<br />\n想搵多啲錢俾啲好啲既治癒俾佢<br />\n有無人有早班或者凌晨既工可以介紹下<br />\n幾辛苦都無所謂"},{"pid":"44f3afe0159c171c6c3bcffb3e7351d180dd9fc3","tid":41323,"uid":3374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:51:08.000Z","msg":"希望伯母無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50db78f35de1789a44042e0e2f9dc80e63bce571","tid":41323,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:54:53.000Z","msg":"快d切左去<br />\n識人十年前有乳癌 切左 (唔記得幾期)<br />\n依家都好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七十歲睇落似五十幾<br />\n陪多d媽媽 等佢樂觀積極d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cb829b87ab33d0655860e1a3aa4bfde4edb5b4","tid":41323,"uid":59736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:55:51.000Z","msg":"2期好易醫 唔駛擔心<br />\n冇錢就去申請資助<br />\n戒口 多休息 多d陪佢就得<br />\n心態最緊要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 我阿媽發現果陣肺癌已經係第4期 暫時相安無事"},{"pid":"6247bbea3bc95b6dce00400b93570deda21aac6d","tid":41323,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T21:13:43.000Z","msg":"雖然冇乜實際幫到手，不過祝伯母吉人天相，早日康復，仲有巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3b877bc460e1119d7ca0af280eec2fc04cd4d7","tid":41323,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T21:50:24.000Z","msg":"祝伯母早日康復 巴打 堅強啲 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a5c2390ef7dc3005b54888b572b49cd190f7ba","tid":41323,"uid":65562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:28:07.000Z","msg":"巴打要頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37310e856084a89ee75683a04083b0ed8c06201e","tid":41323,"uid":37646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:37:49.000Z","msg":"師兄加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efbab97a17ed1e27d8bb7647f17e3db740432e4","tid":41323,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多廢話啦<br />\n我聽過有生癌嘅人係唔洗化療而好返<br />\n你如果真係想佢好<br />\n不如試下搵多D資料先啦"},{"pid":"9a4f973867c3cd2ce2cf032171da3bd8b37626bb","tid":41323,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁多廢話啦<br />\n我聽過有生癌嘅人係唔洗化療而好返<br />\n你如果真係想佢好<br />\n不如試下搵多D資料先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n悲傷唔會令事情好轉<br />\n人生淨係可以不停前進<br />\n你一定要加油<br />\n但千其唔好去太盡"},{"pid":"9e7f975b78390c0c0aaef7aa2c1e6f4485050e9d","tid":41323,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:37:15.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人病真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b22e3e40382e6d09d59192390c8226b97bb163","tid":41323,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:41:05.000Z","msg":"得閒陪下飲茶，周圍行下<br />\n<br />\n心境開朗好大幫助<br />\n<br />\n祝福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107b89f0486c72e570fa205b7fcaf3117ea36acd","tid":41323,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54fc3013935cbb914987a1345f37d965f5a96445","tid":41323,"uid":52410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:44:21.000Z","msg":"遲下叫埋老豆去一家團聚囉"},{"pid":"d10994f3d2c8025f4c08a78da62960b8c3cdf127","tid":41323,"uid":24798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:45:47.000Z","msg":"伯母加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e97a7b7f276f34314db1b0c1b4a83b91e02229","tid":41323,"uid":4090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8ea651901f903363b7e46b45b8400dc6fcebcb1","tid":41323,"uid":15017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2期好易醫 唔駛擔心<br />\n冇錢就去申請資助<br />\n戒口 多休息 多d陪佢就得<br />\n心態最緊要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 我阿媽發現果陣肺癌已經係第4期 暫時相安無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩特別唔食得呀？西醫話其實咩都食得<br />\n有啲又話可以飲豆漿 有啲話唔可以"},{"pid":"fb23c97f1afa3971cc45be7b9bbea137bfba6acb","tid":41323,"uid":15017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人病真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5b31c28eee54efa3d8b09b5f0b338c060fb681","tid":41323,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2期好易醫 唔駛擔心<br />\n冇錢就去申請資助<br />\n戒口 多休息 多d陪佢就得<br />\n心態最緊要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 我阿媽發現果陣肺癌已經係第4期 暫時相安無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩特別唔食得呀？西醫話其實咩都食得<br />\n有啲又話可以飲豆漿 有啲話唔可以</blockquote><br />\n一定唔好食燕窩<br />\n雞同海鮮(特別有殼嗰啲) 多激素都要少食<br />\n豆類製品都係<br />\n仲有奶，芝士嗰啲"}]}